Baroness Ruby was not your average baroness. She was a world-class spy who did not take long to expose Jacob in the tax fraud scheme. Find her entire story at the link in bio. #VersaceHolidaySaga
The Baroness turned out to be a wildly talented singer-songwriter and Angelina immediately signed her to her label, Narcissist Records. Find out more through the link in bio. #VersaceHolidaySaga
In the finale of the #VersaceHolidaySaga the marriage is canceled, Angelo is forgiven and Narcissist Records is saved. Find out what happens with the rest of the characters at the link in bio.

A subversion of the femme fatale genre, the ultimate chapter of the #VersaceHolidaySaga sees Angelina and the Baroness working together to stop Angelo and Jacob’s scheme. Read the story at the link in bio.
